OL,3,CBlack actor who faced death threats
OL,4,Ccalls for industry-wide action
OL,6,FRomeo and Juliet star Francesca
OL,7,FAmewudah-Rivers has called for
OL,8,Findustry-wide action to protect black
OL,9,Fand brown actors from racist abuse,
OL,10,Fafter she revealed that she did not
OL,11,F"feel safe" while working on the West
OL,12,FEnd production.
OL,14,FSpeaking to The Stage about the racist
OL,15,Fbacklash to the announcement of her
OL,16,Flead casting opposite Tom Holland,
OL,17,FAmewudah-Rivers said: "There were many
OL,18,Fdays where I didn't know how I was
OL,19,Fgoing to get through it."
