OL,6,FAs well as online harassment, Amewudah-
OL,7,FRivers said she received hate mail at
OL,8,Fthe Duke of York's Theatre and
OL,9,Femphasised that "the flurry of abuse
OL,10,Fwas sustained throughout the whole
OL,11,Fjob".
OL,13,F"I received death threats, hate mail
OL,14,Fsent to the theatre," she said. "I
OL,15,Fdidn't feel safe at work."
