OL,3,CBlack actor who faced death threats
OL,4,Ccalls for industry-wide action
OL,6,F"I know what it means to move through
OL,7,Flife in a black body. Racism is
OL,8,Fsomething we have to navigate every
OL,9,Fday, so I was very aware of the
OL,10,Fpotential for something like this to
OL,11,Fhappen.
OL,13,F"I think what I was unprepared for was
OL,14,Fhow long it went on for, and also
OL,15,Fhaving to navigate it while doing the
OL,16,Fjob. It was four months of battling
OL,17,Fagainst this energy, and it's
OL,18,Fsomething I still have to deal with.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
