OL,6,F"It is not enough to represent our
OL,7,Fcommunities onstage, there also needs
OL,8,Fto be an infrastructure of support,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"Safety has to be at the forefront. We
OL,12,Fcan't do our best work if we don't
OL,13,Ffeel safe, if we don't feel held, if
OL,14,Fwe don't feel understood."
